lead_paragraph: Serge Ibaka sank two free throws with 1.4 seconds to snap a tie game and send the Orlando Magic to a 103-101 victory over the Philadelphia 76ers on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Magic Rally From 18 Down to Top Winless 76ers 103-101
